snippet: The Mississippi Republican Party says U.S. Sen. Thad Cochran won the state's Republican primary runoff over challenger Chris McDaniel by 7,667 votes....

headline.print_headline: Miss. GOP Certifies Cochran Victory Over McDaniel
headline.main: Miss. GOP Certifies Cochran Victory Over McDaniel

lead_paragraph: The Mississippi Republican Party says U.S. Sen. Thad Cochran won the state's Republican primary runoff over challenger Chris McDaniel by 7,667 votes.
